In [121]:
def hz2w(F, sr):
    NyFreq = sr/2;
    w = F/NyFreq *np.pi;
    return w

def resonance (srate, F, BW):
    a2 = np.exp(-hz2w(BW,srate))
    omega = F*2*np.pi/srate
    a1 = -2*np.sqrt(a2)*np.cos(omega)
    a = np.array([1,a1,a2])
    b = np.array([sum(a)])
    return a, b
